						<summary>

						<p>Another piece of a slab built into the wall of the Rāmaliṅga temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">15th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This broken and damaged slab seems to have recorded a grant of land to the god Baṁmadēva. It mentions the place Sukhadare.</p>						

						<p>It is in characters of the 15th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
